trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInformation" /> class contains information about a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> object and is contained in a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInfoCollection" /> object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInformation" /> 类包含有关 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> 对象的信息，并且包含在 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInfoCollection" /> 对象中。

trans-unit.source: Gets the DNS name of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 获取 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> 对象的 DNS 名称。

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the DNS name of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 一个包含 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> 对象的 DNS 名称的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets the SID of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> object.
A string that contains the SID of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 一个包含 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> 对象的 SID 的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets the NetBIOS name of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 获取 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> 对象的 NetBIOS 名称。

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the NetBIOS name of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 一个包含 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> 对象的 NetBIOS 名称的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the status of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> 对象的状态。

trans-unit.source: One of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainStatus" /> values that represents the status of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainStatus" /> 的一个值，该值表示 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain" /> 对象的状态。
